headline: How The Business First Bancshares (BFST) Story Is Shifting With Modest Analyst Repricing
summary: The fair value price target for Business First Bancshares is set at $32.88, with the latest update keeping this figure unchanged. Analysts have made only modest upward tweaks to their individual price targets, reflecting a recalibration tied to execution on growth, acquisitions, and balance sheet quality rather than a major shift in the story. As you read on, you will see how to track these incremental moves and what they might signal for the evolving analyst narrative around the...

headline: Raymond James Adjusts Mobileye Global Inc. (MBLY) to $16, Cites Earnings Leverage Potential
summary: We recently published an article titled 13 Best Internet of Things (IoT) Stocks to Buy Now. On January 24, Raymond James lowered its price target on Mobileye Global Inc. (NASDAQ:MBLY) to $16 from $19 while maintaining an Outperform rating following fourth-quarter results. The firm reiterated that fiscal 2026 is expected to represent a transitional year […]
